def is_Diff(n):
    even_sum = 0
    odd_sum = 0
    for digit in str(abs(n)):
        if int(digit) % 2 == 0:
            even_sum += int(digit)
        else:
            odd_sum += int(digit)
    return even_sum - odd_sum
```

